string-array.name: tips
string-array.item: "Bona zonke izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza."\n" Thinta isithonjana Sokuqalisa. @drawable/trash"
"Idonsa izinhlelo zokusebenza kwisikrini sakho Sasekhaya. "\n" Thinta & bamba uhlelo lokusebenza Kusiqalisi kuze kube yilapho ludlidliza."
"Hlela kabusha isikrini sakho Sasekhaya "\n" Thinta & ubambe intwana futhi lapho isidlidliza, idonsele lapho ofuna khona."
"Khipha izintwana. "\n" Thinta & bamba intwana futhi lapho isidlidliza, idonsele kwisithonjana Sodoti. @drawable/trash"
"Izikrini Zasekhaya Eziningi."\n"Iya ngakwesokunxele noma esokudla ukushintsha. Donsa izintwana kwezinye izikrini."
"Uqedile ngale wijethi?"\n" Thinta & sibambe futhi lapho sidlidliza, sidonsele kwisithonjana Sodoti."
